question: Within a radius of 90 kilometers, which café can I find on the route towards South 6th St. Community Garden, Philadelphia, PA from West Chester Cardiology, West Chester, PA?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-75.599564 39.969582)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-75.153583 39.935532)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'cafe'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-75.599564 39.969582)',4326)::geography, 90000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-75.599564 39.969582)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
